ps://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/b8/c8/c94d38a7.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1517658340,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":3,"product_id":100003901,"comment_content":"书：1，《微服务设计》，有中文版，偏原理。2，《Spring Microservices in Action》，暂无中文版，原理＋Spring Cloud实战。","like_count":68},{"had_liked":false,"id":2424,"user_name":"朱海峰","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1021494,"ip_address":"","ucode":"D96D2CA8975DBD","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/96/36/0025b51d.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1517172249,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":3,"product_id":100003901,"comment_content":"老师能推荐几本书么","like_count":15},{"had_liked":false,"id":38692,"user_name":"张闯","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1090513,"ip_address":"","ucode":"D5AD46A8DD6FB7","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/a3/d1/a30a4d06.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1542107175,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":3,"product_id":100003901,"comment_content":"架构师需要实现合理的技术架构，好的技术架构一定是与团队人员的组织架构，业务领域的合理拆分一一对应、密不可分的。\n因此，架构师除了要精通相关的技术框架和原理，也需要深谙公司的业务诉求。架构师对业务的理解深度要不亚于产品总监。业务的本质是公司通过自己的产品帮助用户解决某类问题。架构师和产品经理需要从不同的角度共同为解决这个问题寻找方法。\n在理解业务的基础之上才能做出合理的技术架构，技术架构的过程也会加深对业务的理解。此后，架构师也要结合技术架构参与设计技术团队的组织架构。\n三者相辅相成，螺旋上升。","like_count":9},{"had_liked":false,"id":2199,"user_name":"云学","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1027233,"ip_address":"","ucode":"366AE90BA06356","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/ac/a1/43d83698.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1516287932,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":3,"product_id":100003901,"comment_content":"我们公司是集中式软件架构，确是分布式团队，难怪会出问题","like_count":6},{"had_liked":false,"id":53523,"user_name":"花花大脸猫","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":1117318,"ip_address":"","ucode":"8ABDB3F7F4FB0F","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/11/0c/86/8e52afb8.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1545662333,"is_pvip":true,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":3,"product_id":100003901,"comment_content":"请问这个团队跟微服务的规模一般是什么样的比例，比如一个五人的团队对应2-3微服务模块？这个在业界有具体的指标么？","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":351173,"user_name":"Geek5221","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":2961301,"ip_address":"","ucode":"DFC0266FC78A0F","user_header":"","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1657590265,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":3,"product_id":100003901,"comment_content":"#什么是康威法则\n\n最开始是一个叫康威的人，他原来是一个程序员，在1967年的时候提出来。康威法则我们认为它是微服务的理论基础。康威法则的原话是这样讲的，设计系统的组织，其产生的设计和架构等价于组织的组织架构。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":342304,"user_name":"Geek4399","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c3","uid":2961300,"ip_address":"","ucode":"A4185CA5DE47C6","user_header":"","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1650182144,"is_pvip":false,"replies":null,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":3,"product_id":100003901,"comment_content":"康威定律\n  1、组织沟通方式确定系统设计\n  2、时间再多一件事情也不可能做的完美，但中有时间做完一件事情\n  3、线型系统和线型组织架构间有潜在的异质同态特性 （要什么系统就搭建什么样的团队，有什么样的团队就搭建什么样的系统）\n   4、大的系统组织中是比小系统更倾向于分解","like_count":0}]}